data.description: Step into this enchanting Victorian home and be captivated by its timeless charm. Marvel at the marble floor entry as you journey through each room, where unique character unfolds at every turn. This three-bedroom, two-bathroom Victorian beauty boasts well-loved original woodwork that adds a touch of nostalgia to its spacious interiors. The updated, bright kitchen beckons with modern allure, complemented by the warmth of hardwood floors throughout. Picture yourself sipping a cup of tea on the completely covered porch or enjoying the serenity of your private master bedroom balcony. Noteworthy is the rarity of the front primary bedroom balcony-a feature that sets this home apart. A full unfinished basement and a detached garage built in 2012 provide ample storage, ensuring convenience meets style in this delightful abode. Perfect for entertaining, the home showcases updated windows while preserving much of its original character and charm. Step into the fully fenced privacy backyard, a serene retreat that completes this charming residence. Don't miss the chance to make this your own; call today for a private showing and experience the allure of Victorian living.
